<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dry-v">dry <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /draɪ/    美 /draɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 变干；(把...) 弄干：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Dry it in the air / in the sun.
晾干/晒干。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>dry one’s tears / eyes</strong>
擦干眼泪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nylon dries quickly.
尼龙织物干得快。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="dry-off">dry off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(使) 变干；(把…) 弄干</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="dry-out">dry out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(使) 完全变干；干透</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="dry-up">dry up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(河流、湖泊等) 干涸：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Over the centuries, the water dried up.
经过几个世纪，水完全干了。</p></div></div>